  "planContent": "# 🏗️ Architecture Blueprint\n\n## App Overview\n\"The Tactile Studio\" is a visual-first digital gallery application for managing, viewing, and organizing artistic sketches. It provides a clean, high-fidelity interface for artists to browse their creative collection and trigger the creation of new works, leveraging a responsive Bento grid layout.\n\n## Core Features\n- **Gallery Dashboard**: Grid-based display of all saved sketches with titles and metadata.\n- **Responsive Bento Grid**: Dynamic scaling (1-3 columns) based on viewport width.\n- **Sketch Interaction**: Hover-to-zoom effect on images; persistent shadow styling.\n- **Navigation Hub**: Bottom persistent nav bar for switching between Canvas, Gallery, and Settings.\n- **Action Interface**: Floating Action Button (FAB) for quick-triggering a new sketch creation workflow.\n- **Offline Persistence**: Auto-save architecture using internal indexedDB interface.\n\n## UI & Layout Strategy\n- **Layout type**: Single-page application with fixed headers and footers.\n- **Header**: Top app bar containing the \"Tactile Studio\" title and a \"Save\" action button.\n- **Main content area**: Centered max-width container with a `grid` layout for gallery cards.\n- **Controls**: Persistent FAB (bottom-right) for adding new items; bottom navigation bar (fixed).\n- **Footer**: Branding integrated within the bottom navigation layout.\n- **Design System**: Exact Tailwind classes provided in the reference (primary: #0058bc, background: #f7f5ff).\n- **Color scheme**: Custom palette defined in `tailwind.config` (Surface: #f7f5ff, Primary: #0058bc, On-Surface: #242c51).\n- **Responsive strategy**: Mobile (1 col) to Tablet (2 col) to Desktop (3 col). FAB visibility is persistent across all breakpoints.\n- **Animations & UX**: Tailwind transitions on hover (scale-105 for images, scale-110 for FAB). `backdrop-blur-xl` for header.\n- **Touch Targets**: Min 44px height for all interactive elements (buttons, nav tabs).\n- **Accessibility**: ARIA labels for buttons; focus rings (standardized `focus:ring-2` for keyboard accessibility).\n\n## Data Model & State\n| Variable | Type | Default | Description |\n|----------|------|---------|-------------|\n| sketches | Array<{id, title, date, src}> | [] | Core gallery dataset |\n| activeTab | String | 'gallery' | Tracks current nav position |\n| isLoading | Boolean | true | Controls loading state of images |\n\n- **Persistence Strategy**: Use `window.forge.db.set('sketches', 'list', data)` on every update. `window.forge.db.get` invoked on initialization to hydrate `sketches` array.\n\n## Technical Stack & Libraries\n- **Required CDNs**: Tailwind CSS (with plugins), Material Symbols Outlined, Google Fonts (Plus Jakarta Sans, Be Vietnam Pro, Manrope).\n- **Allowed**: Tailwind CSS, Lucide Icons (as fallback or supplement), Material Symbols.\n- **APIs**: None (100% offline-first).\n\n## Implementation Steps\n1. Step 1: Initialize HTML5 boilerplate with strict `<meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"no-referrer\">` in head.\n2. Step 2: Implement the `tailwind.config` exactly as provided in the source code.\n3. Step 3: Set up global styles (min-height, fonts, base colors).\n4. Step 4: Construct the fixed header component with backdrop-blur.\n5. Step 5: Build the bottom navigation bar and link click-handlers to state switching.\n6. Step 6: Implement the `sketches` state management logic and `forge.db` integration.\n7. Step 7: Create the dynamic Bento grid component that maps over the `sketches` array.\n8. Step 8: Build the card component with `referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"` for all `<img>` tags.\n9. Step 9: Add the FAB component with hover-to-show text logic.\n10. Step 10: Finalize event listeners for \"Save\" button and state synchronization.\n\n## Edge Cases & Error Handling\n- **Empty state**: Display a \"No sketches found\" message with an illustration if `sketches` is empty.\n- **Image failure**: Add a `onerror` fallback image or skeleton state to prevent layout collapse.\n- **Data corruption**: Implement a `try-catch` wrapper around `forge.db` operations; fallback to empty array on read failure.\n- **Mobile scaling**: Ensure FAB does not overlap with bottom navigation on small screens by adding `pb-32` padding to `body`.",
  "currentHTML": "<file path=\"settings.html\">\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"no-referrer\">\n    <title>Settings - The Tactile Studio</title>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries\"></script>\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Be+Vietnam+Pro:wght@400;500;600&family=Manrope:wght@500;600;700;800&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n    <script src=\"/forge.js\"></script>\n    <script>\n        tailwind.config = {\n            theme: {\n                extend: {\n                    colors: {\n                        \"primary\": \"#0058bc\",\n                        \"background\": \"#f7f5ff\",\n                        \"on-surface\": \"#242c51\",\n                        \"on-surface-variant\": \"#515981\",\n                        \"surface-container-lowest\": \"#ffffff\",\n                        \"surface-container\": \"#e4e7ff\",\n                        \"primary-fixed\": \"#6d9fff\",\n                        \"on-primary-fixed\": \"#000000\"\n                    },\n                    fontFamily: {\n                        \"headline\": [\"Plus Jakarta Sans\"],\n                        \"body\": [\"Be Vietnam Pro\"],\n                        \"label\": [\"Manrope\"]\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    </script>\n    <style>\n        .material-symbols-outlined { font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24; }\n        body { font-family: 'Be Vietnam Pro', sans-serif; background-color: #f7f5ff; color: #242c51; min-height: 100dvh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"pb-32\">\n    <header class=\"fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-xl flex justify-between items-center px-6 py-4 shadow-xl shadow-blue-900/5\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\">\n            <h1 class=\"font-headline font-extrabold text-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent\">The Tactile Studio</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"pt-24 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto flex-grow w-full\">\n        <div class=\"mb-8\">\n            <h2 class=\"font-headline text-3xl font-extrabold text-on-surface\">Settings</h2>\n            <p class=\"font-body text-sm text-on-surface-variant mt-2\">Manage your app preferences and data.</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"space-y-6\">\n            <!-- Profile Settings -->\n            <div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/5\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-headline text-lg font-bold text-on-surface flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\">\n                    <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">person</span> Profile\n                </h3>\n                <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                    <div>\n                        <label class=\"block font-label text-sm font-bold text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Display Name</label>\n                        <input type=\"text\" id=\"display-name\" class=\"w-full rounded-lg border-gray-200 focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary text-sm\" placeholder=\"Enter your name\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                        <label class=\"block font-label text-sm font-bold text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Email Address</label>\n                        <input type=\"email\" id=\"email-address\" class=\"w-full rounded-lg border-gray-200 focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary text-sm\" placeholder=\"you@example.com\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Preferences -->\n            <div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/5\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-headline text-lg font-bold text-on-surface flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\">\n                    <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">palette</span> Preferences\n                </h3>\n                <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                    <label class=\"flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer group\">\n                        <span class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">High Quality Canvas Rendering</span>\n                        <div class=\"relative\">\n                            <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"hq-render\" class=\"sr-only peer\">\n                            <div class=\"w-11 h-6 bg-gray-200 peer-focus:outline-none peer-focus:ring-4 peer-focus:ring-blue-300 rounded-full peer peer-checked:after:translate-x-full peer-checked:after:border-white after:content-[''] after:absolute after:top-[2px] after:left-[2px] after:bg-white after:border-gray-300 after:border after:rounded-full after:h-5 after:w-5 after:transition-all peer-checked:bg-primary\"></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </label>\n                    <label class=\"flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer group\">\n                        <span class=\"font-body text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Auto-save Sketches</span>\n                        <div class=\"relative\">\n                            <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"auto-save\" class=\"sr-only peer\" checked>\n                            <div class=\"w-11 h-6 bg-gray-200 peer-focus:outline-none peer-focus:ring-4 peer-focus:ring-blue-300 rounded-full peer peer-checked:after:translate-x-full peer-checked:after:border-white after:content-[''] after:absolute after:top-[2px] after:left-[2px] after:bg-white after:border-gray-300 after:border after:rounded-full after:h-5 after:w-5 after:transition-all peer-checked:bg-primary\"></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </label>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Data Management -->\n            <div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/5\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-headline text-lg font-bold text-on-surface flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\">\n                    <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">database</span> Data Management\n                </h3>\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-4\">Export your gallery data or clear all local storage.</p>\n                <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3\">\n                    <button onclick=\"saveSettings()\" class=\"bg-primary text-white font-bold px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full sm:w-auto\">\n                        <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-sm\">save</span> Save Settings\n                    </button>\n                    <button onclick=\"clearData()\" class=\"bg-red-50 text-red-600 font-bold px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-100 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full sm:w-auto\">\n                        <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-sm\">delete</span> Clear All Data\n                    </button>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n\n    <nav class=\"fixed bottom-0 left-0 w-full flex justify-around items-center px-4 pb-6 pt-3 bg-[#efefff] rounded-t-[2.5rem] z-50 shadow-[0_-10px_40px_rgba(36,44,81,0.06)]\">\n        <a href=\"canvas.html\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-slate-400 p-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">brush</span><span class=\"text-[11px] uppercase mt-1\">Canvas</span></a>\n        <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-slate-400 p-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">grid_view</span><span class=\"text-[11px] uppercase mt-1\">Gallery</span></a>\n        <a href=\"settings.html\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-blue-700 bg-white rounded-2xl px-6 py-2 shadow-sm\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\" style=\"font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;\">settings</span><span class=\"text-[11px] uppercase mt-1\">Settings</span></a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <footer class=\"text-center p-4 text-neutral-400 text-xs opacity-80 flex justify-center items-center gap-1.5 mt-auto\">\n        <span>Built with</span> \n        <img src=\"https://forge-app.vercel.app/logo.png\" alt=\"Forge\" class=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-sm object-cover\"> \n        <a href=\"https://forge-app.vercel.app\" class=\"text-blue-500 font-semibold tracking-wide no-underline\">FORGE</a>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        async function loadSettings() {\n            try {\n                const settings = await window.forge.db.get('tactile_studio', 'settings') || {\n                    displayName: '',\n                    email: '',\n                    hqRender: false,\n                    autoSave: true\n                };\n                \n                document.getElementById('display-name').value = settings.displayName || '';\n                document.getElementById('email-address').value = settings.email || '';\n                document.getElementById('hq-render').checked = settings.hqRender || false;\n                document.getElementById('auto-save').checked = settings.autoSave !== false;\n            } catch (e) {\n                console.error(\"Failed to load settings:\", e);\n            }\n        }\n\n        async function saveSettings() {\n            const settings = {\n                displayName: document.getElementById('display-name').value,\n                email: document.getElementById('email-address').value,\n                hqRender: document.getElementById('hq-render').checked,\n                autoSave: document.getElementById('auto-save').checked\n            };\n            \n            await window.forge.db.set('tactile_studio', 'settings', settings);\n            \n            const btn = document.querySelector('button[onclick=\"saveSettings()\"]');\n            const originalText = btn.innerHTML;\n            btn.innerHTML = `<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-sm\">check</span> Saved!`;\n            btn.classList.add('bg-green-600');\n            \n            setTimeout(() => {\n                btn.innerHTML = originalText;\n                btn.classList.remove('bg-green-600');\n            }, 2000);\n        }\n\n        async function clearData() {\n            if(confirm(\"Are you sure you want to delete all sketches and settings? This cannot be undone.\")) {\n                await window.forge.db.set('tactile_studio', 'default', []);\n                await window.forge.db.set('tactile_studio', 'settings', null);\n                alert(\"All data cleared successfully.\");\n                loadSettings();\n            }\n        }\n\n        loadSettings();\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n</file>\n<file path=\"index.html\">\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"no-referrer\">\n    <title>The Tactile Studio</title>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries\"></script>\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Be+Vietnam+Pro:wght@400;500;600&family=Manrope:wght@500;600;700;800&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n    <script src=\"/forge.js\"></script>\n    <script>\n        tailwind.config = {\n            theme: {\n                extend: {\n                    colors: {\n                        \"primary\": \"#0058bc\",\n                        \"background\": \"#f7f5ff\",\n                        \"on-surface\": \"#242c51\",\n                        \"on-surface-variant\": \"#515981\",\n                        \"surface-container-lowest\": \"#ffffff\",\n                        \"surface-container\": \"#e4e7ff\",\n                        \"primary-fixed\": \"#6d9fff\",\n                        \"on-primary-fixed\": \"#000000\"\n                    },\n                    fontFamily: {\n                        \"headline\": [\"Plus Jakarta Sans\"],\n                        \"body\": [\"Be Vietnam Pro\"],\n                        \"label\": [\"Manrope\"]\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    </script>\n    <style>\n        .material-symbols-outlined { font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24; }\n        body { font-family: 'Be Vietnam Pro', sans-serif; background-color: #f7f5ff; color: #242c51; min-height: 100dvh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"pb-32\">\n    <header class=\"fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-xl flex justify-between items-center px-6 py-4 shadow-xl shadow-blue-900/5\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\">\n            <h1 class=\"font-headline font-extrabold text-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent\">The Tactile Studio</h1>\n        </div>\n        <button onclick=\"saveData()\" class=\"text-blue-600 font-bold px-4 py-1 rounded-full hover:bg-blue-50 transition-all active:scale-95\">Save</button>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"pt-24 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto flex-grow w-full\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-baseline justify-between mb-8\">\n            <h2 class=\"font-headline text-3xl font-extrabold text-on-surface\">Your Gallery</h2>\n            <span id=\"sketch-count\" class=\"font-label text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest\">0 Sketches</span>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div id=\"gallery-grid\" class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n            <!-- Dynamic Content -->\n        </div>\n    </main>\n\n    <button onclick=\"addMockSketch()\" class=\"fixed bottom-32 right-8 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-primary-fixed shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-on-primary-fixed hover:scale-110 transition-all z-40 group\">\n        <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-3xl\">add</span>\n        <div class=\"absolute right-full mr-4 bg-on-surface text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity whitespace-nowrap pointer-events-none\">New Sketch</div>\n    </button>\n\n    <nav class=\"fixed bottom-0 left-0 w-full flex justify-around items-center px-4 pb-6 pt-3 bg-[#efefff] rounded-t-[2.5rem] z-50 shadow-[0_-10px_40px_rgba(36,44,81,0.06)]\">\n        <a href=\"canvas.html\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-slate-400 p-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">brush</span><span class=\"text-[11px] uppercase mt-1\">Canvas</span></a>\n        <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-blue-700 bg-white rounded-2xl px-6 py-2 shadow-sm\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\" style=\"font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;\">grid_view</span><span class=\"text-[11px] uppercase mt-1\">Gallery</span></a>\n        <a href=\"settings.html\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-slate-400 p-2 hover:text-primary transition-colors\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">settings</span><span class=\"text-[11px] uppercase mt-1\">Settings</span></a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <footer class=\"text-center p-4 text-neutral-400 text-xs opacity-80 flex justify-center items-center gap-1.5 mt-auto\"><span>Built with</span> <img src=\"https://forge-app.vercel.app/logo.png\" alt=\"Forge\" class=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-sm object-cover\"> <a href=\"https://forge-app.vercel.app\" class=\"text-blue-500 font-semibold tracking-wide no-underline\">FORGE</a></footer>\n\n    <script>\n        let sketches = [];\n\n        async function init() {\n            try {\n                sketches = await window.forge.db.get('tactile_studio', 'default') || [];\n            } catch (e) {\n                sketches = [];\n            }\n            render();\n        }\n\n        async function saveData() {\n            await window.forge.db.set('tactile_studio', 'default', sketches);\n            alert(\"Gallery Saved!\");\n        }\n\n        function addMockSketch() {\n            const newSketch = {\n                id: Date.now(),\n                title: \"New Exploration \" + (sketches.length + 1),\n                date: new Date().toLocaleDateString(),\n                src: \"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1549490349-8643362247b5?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600\"\n            };\n            sketches.push(newSketch);\n            render();\n        }\n\n        function render() {\n            const container = document.getElementById('gallery-grid');\n            const countEl = document.getElementById('sketch-count');\n            countEl.textContent = `${sketches.length} Sketches`;\n            \n            if (sketches.length === 0) {\n                container.innerHTML = `<div class=\"col-span-full py-20 text-center text-on-surface-variant\">No sketches found. Create your first one!</div>`;\n                return;\n            }\n\n            container.innerHTML = sketches.map(s => `\n                <div class=\"group relative bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg p-4 shadow-lg transition-all duration-300\">\n                    <div class=\"aspect-[4/3] rounded-md overflow-hidden bg-surface-container mb-4\">\n                        <img src=\"${s.src}\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500\" alt=\"${s.title}\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"px-2 flex justify-between items-start\">\n                        <div>\n                            <h3 class=\"font-body text-lg font-bold text-on-surface\">${s.title}</h3>\n                            <p class=\"font-label text-xs font-semibold text-on-surface-variant/70 uppercase mt-1\">${s.date}</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <button onclick=\"deleteSketch(${s.id})\" class=\"text-slate-300 hover:text-red-500 transition-colors p-1\">\n                            <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]\">delete</span>\n                        </button>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            `).join('');\n        }\n\n        function deleteSketch(id) {\n            if(confirm(\"Delete this sketch?\")) {\n                sketches = sketches.filter(s => s.id !== id);\n                render();\n                saveData(); // Auto save on delete\n            }\n        }\n\n        init();\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n</file>",
